curl Copy <pre><code>curl --request POST \
    "https://appambitv2-restless-morning-3748.fly.dev/api/analytics" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_KEY}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data '{
    "analytics": {
        "event_title": "\"Member Data Loaded\"",
        "session_id": "1",
        "data": "[{ \"a\": \"b\" }, {\"x\": \"y\"}]"
    }
}'</code></pre>

json Copy <pre><code>{
  "analytics": {
    "event_title": "\"Member Data Loaded\"",
    "session_id": "1",
    "data": "[{ \"a\": \"b\" }, {\"x\": \"y\"}]"
  }
}</code></pre> Note: The <code>data</code> field is a JSON string containing an array of objects. Ensure proper escaping when constructing the request body.
